```

Save it (`Ctrl + S`).

**Why `artifacts/` is gitignored:**
- `model.pkl` can be 100MB+ — GitHub has a 100MB file limit
- In CI/CD, artifacts get **regenerated** by running the pipeline — they are never stored in git
- Only your **code** goes to GitHub, not your trained models

---

